%% Diagram: Soft vs hard purge — timing of cache state and origin load after a purge call
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as App / CMS
    participant CDN
    participant Origin
    participant User

    Note over App,User: Hard purge — content removed instantly
    App->>CDN: Purge key=p-123 (hard)
    Note over CDN: Entry deleted, key now MISS
    User->>CDN: GET /products/123
    CDN->>Origin: Synchronous fetch (blocks user)
    Origin-->>CDN: 200 OK fresh
    CDN-->>User: 200 OK fresh

    Note over App,User: Soft purge — content marked stale
    App->>CDN: Purge key=p-123 (soft)
    Note over CDN: Entry kept, marked stale (SWR / SIE eligible)
    User->>CDN: GET /products/123
    CDN-->>User: 200 OK STALE (instant)
    CDN->>Origin: Async revalidate (background)
    Origin-->>CDN: 200 OK fresh
    Note over CDN: Entry replaced
